1. *Košulja* mi je neugodno zategnuta oko vrata. (My *shirt* is uncomfortably tight around my neck.)
2. Ovaj prodavač ima stotinu različitih modela *košulja*. (This salesman has a hundred different models of *shirts*.)
3. Sinoć sam oprala tri *košulje* i objesila ih da se suše. (Last night, I washed three *shirts* and hung them to dry.)
4. Molim vas, odnesite ovu *košulju* na kemijsko čišćenje. (Please take this *shirt* to the dry cleaners.)
5. Ne nosi uvijek bijelu *košulju*, pokušaj nešto drugačije. (Don't always wear a white *shirt*, try something different.)
6. Ova *košulja* mi je omiljena zbog svog mekanog materijala. (This *shirt* is my favorite because of its soft material.)
7. Kada bih imao više novca, kupio bih ovu skupu *košulju*. (If I had more money, I would buy this expensive *shirt*.)
8. Žena je pomogla svom mužu da obuče *košulju* za večeru. (The woman helped her husband put on his *shirt* for dinner.)
9. *Košulja* mu je bila poderana na ramenu i morao ju je baciti. (His *shirt* was torn on the shoulder and he had to throw it away.)
10. Izgledaš vrlo lijepo u toj plavoj *košulji*. (You look very nice in that blue *shirt*.)